『双鱼玉佩』
[[span style="opacity: 90%"]]『红衣女孩』[[/span]]
[[span style="opacity: 70%"]]『太平间的红带子』[[/span]]
[[span style="opacity: 50%"]]『买命钱』[[/span]]
[[span style="opacity: 30%"]]『不动的孔夫子像』[[/span]]
[[span style="opacity: 20%"]]『纸嫁衣』[[/span]]
